we are the gateway to creativity and innovationtransform at silicon valley's public universitywhen you become a student at san jos state, youre not only embarking on a transformative college journey youre joining a new, extended spartan family. sjsu is a diverse, close-knit community with access to cutting-edge research, world-class scholarship and transformative opportunities that advance the public good locally and globally.majors and programssan jos state provides a wide range of undergraduate programs, with both online and in-person courses, that promote intellectual inquiry and independent thought.sjsu onlinealso offers five fully online degree completion programs.tuition and feessan jos state is dedicated to providing affordable access to high-quality education at the fraction of the cost learn more about tuition, meal plans, financial aid and scholarships.degree roadmapsee what the roadmap looks like to stay on track to graduate in four years for first-year students and two years for transfers.housingfrom traditional residence halls to greek houses and downtown apartments, san jos state offers multiple housing options that will fit your needs.campus lifethrough shared experiences with peers, service to the community, and acts of creation, recreation and cohabitation, discover what san jos state has to offer beyond the classroom.connect with a counselorneed help planning your journey to san jos state or just have some questions? our admission counselors are ready to help.covid-19 safety protocolssan jos states health advisories site provides the latest information on the universitys response to the covid-19 pandemic. this includes compliance with the csus vaccination policy, information on safety protocols and frequently asked questions.sjsu caressjsu cares provides you the resources and services for any type of financial crisis you may face during your journey at san jos state from having trouble paying for food, housing or other bills, we are always here to help.health and wellness resourcestaking care of your health and wellness is critical to your academic success. at san jos state, we provide a variety of resources to help you take care of all the dimensions of wellness: physical, social, emotional, occupational, multicultural, environmental, spiritual and intellectual.dedication to diversity, equity and inclusionsan jos state is unique in its long history of student civil rights activism, service to first-generation student populations and racial and ethnic diversity. sjsu's office of diversity, equity and inclusion works to create a campus community that is free from discrimination and systemic and cultural barriers to your academic success.commitment to sustainabilitywe offer a wide range of academic courses and programs related to sustainability, as well as ongoing campus-wide efforts to minimize san jos states "ecological footprint" by reducing campus energy consumption, water use, and waste.support for local communitywith san jos state located in the heart of the city, weve created the sjsu loves sj initiative in collaboration with downtown organizations and san jos city hall to further connect and integrate students with the culture of the thriving local community.every spartan emerges career readysee where your degree from silicon valleys public university can take you. build relevant career experience by tapping into our network of over 9,000 local and 30,000 global employers that seek sjsu students.stories of transformation at sjsua university education can be measured in many ways, such as in degrees earned, years of study accomplished, money spent or saved, lifelong friendships made, or mentorships and relationships formed. san jos state university was named the #1 most transformative university in the nation by money magazine, in part, because spartans say that sjsu has helped them transform and effect positive change, not only for themselves but also for their communities.marielle lacanlale22 nursingif i had not gone to sjsu to pursue nursing, i would not have been able to develop the work ethic that i have now to achieve my goals. sjsu has also provided me with a very strong filipino community. now that i am in the nursing school here, sjsu has provided me with so many opportunities to make a difference within my community.tommy wen chin22 physics[my sjsu professor] gave me the courage that i had been longing for to pursue physics. every day since then, i have been very grateful for the opportunity to pursue what i truly love.alexandra salazar20 molecular biologycoming to sjsu introduced me to the mentors that would see my potential and help transform me into the scientist i am becoming. thanks to the resources and guidance i received at sjsu, i will begin pursuing my phd in neuroscience at the scripps research institute starting fall 2021.#1 most transformative universityranked bymagazine based on graduation rates, earnings and student loan repayment.#8 best value schoolsranked bybased on academic quality and net cost of attendance.#13 top colleges for diversity in the nationranked by(wsj/the) among colleges and universities in the nation for diversity in school environments.requirements and next steps for admissionlearn more about gpa and course requirements or register for our next workshop to learn how to fill out an application for san jos state.join our communitystay up to date with what's going on at san jos state, what our students are up to, enrollment information and campus updates by following us on social media.interested in applying to an undergraduate program or visiting campus, visit ourundergraduate student outreach and recruitment office website.interested in applying to a graduate program or have questions about applying, visit ourgraduate enrollment management office website.408-283-7500monday to friday 9:00 a.m. - 4:00 p.m.(icon at the bottom right corner)monday - friday, 9 a.m. - 12 noon and 2 - 4 p.m.bachelor's degrees and undergraduate adm